lead_paragraph: China on Monday downplayed an accusation by U.S. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton that Beijing had tried to "hack into everything that doesn't move in America".

headline.main: China Downplays Hillary Clinton Claim It Hacked U.S. Information
